The short corridor is equipped with mirrors on both sides, making it look longer.
The mirror rails in the kitchen look like a window to the next room.
At the entrance door there are storage rooms equipped with mirrors for storing cutlery and glasses.
The advantage of the living room, which gives the whole apartment the impression of a significantly larger space, is the ability to separate it from the kitchen, if not used.
